org.eclipse.compare.structuremergeviewer

Interface IStructureComparator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DocumentRangeNode, ResourceNode, StructureRootNode

    public interface IStructureComparator
    Interface used to compare hierarchical structures. It is used by the differencing engine.

    Clients typically implement this interface in an adaptor class which wrappers the objects to be compared.

    See Also:
    ResourceNode, Differencer
